{
  "texts": [
    "The question arises whether Bitcoin will experience a revival with the Lightning network.",
    "When transmitted via the Lightning network, there is no real distinction between layer one and layer two solutions.",
    "Additionally, Bitcoin has been striving to increase the use of renewable energy and improve speed and user-friendliness for everyday transactions.",
    "Perhaps, there is potential for new blockchain innovations to emerge from Bitcoin.",
    "In summary, the Internet has evolved from Web1 to Web2, and the anticipated arrival of Web3 brings new uncertainties regarding platform dominance and the emergence of innovative cryptocurrencies."
  ]
}